---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="AI for E-Commerce | Scott Armbruster" description="Recover abandoned carts, automate customer support, and personalize shopping experiences with AI built for online stores.">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="pt-32 pb-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <p class="text-blue-400 text-sm font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase mb-6">
          AI for E-Commerce
        </p>

        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight">
          Sell More,
          <br />
          <span class="text-white">
            Support Less
          </span>
        </h1>

        <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl text-slate-200 mb-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto font-light">
          AI automation that recovers revenue and cuts support costs for online stores
        </p>

        <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          70% of shopping carts get abandoned. Your support team answers the same 10 questions
          200 times a month. AI fixes both problems while you sleep.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold transition inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2"
          >
            Book Free Discovery Call
          </a>
          <a
            href="/calculators/chatbot-roi"
            class="bg-slate-800 hover:bg-slate-700 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold transition inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2"
          >
            Calculate Your ROI
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Use Cases -->
  <section class="py-20 px-6 bg-slate-900/50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">AI That Pays for Itself in Week One</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-300">
          These are the highest-ROI automations for online stores
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-8">
          <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-blue-400 mb-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 3h2l.4 2M7 13h10l4-8H5.4M7 13L5.4 5M7 13l-2.293 2.293c-.63.63-.184 1.707.707 1.707H17m0 0a2 2 0 100 4 2 2 0 000-4zm-8 2a2 2 0 100 4 2 2 0 000-4z"/>
          </svg>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Cart Abandonment Recovery</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm">
            AI chatbot engages visitors before they leave. Answers product questions, offers help, and reduces cart abandonment by 15-25%.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-8">
          <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-blue-400 mb-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z"/>
          </svg>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">24/7 Customer Support</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm">
            Handle order status, shipping questions, returns, and sizing inquiries automatically. Resolve 60-80% of tickets without human involvement.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-8">
          <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-blue-400 mb-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 7h.01M7 3h5c.512 0 1.024.195 1.414.586l7 7a2 2 0 010 2.828l-7 7a2 2 0 01-2.828 0l-7-7A1.994 1.994 0 013 12V7a4 4 0 014-4z"/>
          </svg>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Product Recommendations</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm">
            AI suggests relevant products based on browsing behavior and purchase history. Increase average order value by 10-20%.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-8">
          <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-blue-400 mb-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M11 5H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v11a2 2 0 002 2h11a2 2 0 002-2v-5m-1.414-9.414a2 2 0 112.828 2.828L11.828 15H9v-2.828l8.586-8.586z"/>
          </svg>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Product Descriptions</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm">
            Generate SEO-optimized product descriptions at scale. Feed in specs and features, get compelling copy that converts.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-8">
          <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-blue-400 mb-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
          </svg>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Post-Purchase Flows</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm">
            Automated review requests, cross-sell sequences, and re-engagement campaigns personalized to each customer's purchase history.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-8">
          <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-blue-400 mb-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"/>
          </svg>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Inventory & Pricing</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm">
            AI monitors demand patterns and competitor pricing to suggest optimal stock levels and pricing adjustments.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-20 px-6 border-t border-slate-800/60">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Every Hour Your Store Runs Without AI, You Lose Money</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 mb-8">
        Book a free discovery call. I'll audit your store's biggest leaks and show you
        which AI automations will have the fastest payback.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold transition"
        >
          Book Discovery Call
        </a>
        <a
          href="/guarantee"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-slate-800 hover:bg-slate-700 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold transition"
        >
          See the 90-Day Guarantee
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
